---
title: Mustard-Fig Roasted Turkey with Stone Fruit, Potato-Brussels Sprout Mash and Broccolini
description: Mustard-fig-glazed turkey breast is roasted to perfection and served with tender broccolini and a Brussels spout-studded mash. But, it's the fresh stone fruit salsa that truly makes this dinner a summery feast!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/mustard-fig-roasted-turkey-7fca434d.jpg
